premise_source_doc_sentence: Abigail `` Abby '' Sciuto -LSB- ˈʃuːtoʊ -RSB- is a fictional character from the NCIS television series on CBS Television , and is portrayed by Pauley Perrette .
Pauley Perrette  (  born March 27 , 1969  )  is an American actress , best known for playing Abby Sciuto on the U.S. TV series NCIS .

MI6 agent Clayton Reeves  (  Duane Henry  )  , forensic specialist Abby Sciuto  (  Pauley Perrette  )  , and medical examiners Dr Jimmy Palmer  (  Brian Dietzen  )  and Dr Donald `` Ducky '' Mallard  (  David McCallum  )  also assist the team during these troubled times , while Directors Tom Morrow  (  Alan Dale  )  , Jennifer Shepard  (  Lauren Holly  )  , and Leon Vance  (  Rocky Carroll  )  watch from on-high .
